Deepin UI Toolkit for Linux Deepin.

WARNING: for Debian base system, please install below packages 
		python-gtk2_2.24.0-3deepin1_amd64.deb
		python-glade2_2.24.0-3deepin1_amd64.deb 
first, otherwise, you will got memory leak (this is bug of python-gtk).

* Deepin UI build dependence (Debian):
  sudo apt-get install libc6 libcairo2 libglib2.0-dev libsoup2.4-1 libwebkitgtk-dev debconf python libgtk2.0-0 python-gtk2 python-imaging python-xlib python-scipy python-setuptools

* Install Deepin UI:
  sudo python setup.py install

* Build API docs:
  ./repos.sh build_html
  ./repos.sh build_pdf

